## IAM Roles & Policies

```
# Mobile Client Role (for iOS app)
MOBILE_CLIENT_ROLE_NAME=ConnectMobileClientRole
MOBILE_CLIENT_ROLE_ARN=arn:aws:iam::123456789012:role/ConnectMobileClientRole

# Agent App Role (for Android app)
AGENT_APP_ROLE_NAME=ConnectAgentAppRole
AGENT_APP_ROLE_ARN=arn:aws:iam::123456789012:role/ConnectAgentAppRole

# API User (for backend)
API_USER_NAME=mobile-app-user
API_USER_ACCESS_KEY=AKIA...
API_USER_SECRET_KEY=...                # ⚠️ KEEP SECRET!
```

