## Backend/Lambda Configuration

```
# Lambda Function
LAMBDA_FUNCTION_NAME=amazon-connect-presigner
LAMBDA_FUNCTION_ARN=arn:aws:lambda:us-east-1:123456789012:function:amazon-connect-presigner
LAMBDA_RUNTIME=python3.9

# S3 Configuration
S3_BUCKET_NAME=connect-recordings-bucket
S3_RECORDINGS_PREFIX=recordings/
S3_LOGS_PREFIX=logs/
S3_ENCRYPTION_KEY_ID=arn:aws:kms:us-east-1:123456789012:key/xxxxxxxx-xxxx-xxxx-xxxx-xxxxxxxxxxxx

# CloudWatch Configuration
CLOUDWATCH_LOG_GROUP=/aws/lambda/amazon-connect-presigner
CLOUDWATCH_LOG_RETENTION_DAYS=7
CLOUDWATCH_NAMESPACE=AmazonConnect/Mobile
```

